highlights.text: “Dynamite” by BTS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Come & Go (with Marshmello)” is the highest at #16.
“Lean” by Super Yei, Sammy, Jone Quest, Towy, Osquel, Beltito, and Sammy & Falsetto is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 52 spots at #96.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 190 weeks straight.
